  "text": "Reflection is effective in separating the development of parts of code of different nature, while providing the necessary connection between them at run-time. Reflective systems have been proposed to separate typical application functionalities from supplementary concerns such as synchronisation [CITATION_1] , distribution [CITATION_2] , etc.",
